"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-23-france-intercepting-6-drones-daily-near-olympic-sites-pm\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"V\\u00c9LIZY-VILLACOUBLAY, France (AFP)- French security forces guarding sites set to be used in the Paris Olympics are intercepting an average of six drones per day, Prime Minister Gabriel Attal said.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.997274190735678, \"rank\": 0.0027259829861926124, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 176, \"end\": 189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Attal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Attal\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Attal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Attal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"French security forces\", \"from\": 35, \"to\": 57}, {\"ngram\": \"sites\", \"from\": 67, \"to\": 72}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 109}, {\"ngram\": \"an average\", \"from\": 127, \"to\": 137}, {\"ngram\": \"six drones\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 151}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The miniature flyers are sometimes operated by \\\"individuals, maybe tourists wanting to take pictures\\\", Attal said.\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The miniature flyers\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 217}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 256}, {\"ngram\": \"pictures\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"Attal\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's why it's important to remind people of the rules.\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a ban on flying drones,\\\" he added during a visit to the event's drone defence hub at Velizy-Villacoublay air base outside Paris.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999247393, \"rank\": 7.520899155955478e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a ban\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"flying drones\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 402}, {\"ngram\": \"a visit\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"the event's drone defence hub\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"Velizy-Villacoublay air base\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Systems are in place to allow us to very quickly intercept (drones) and arrest their operators,\\\" Attal said.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Systems\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 543}, {\"ngram\": \"drones\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 577}, {\"ngram\": \"their operators\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"Attal\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We can not allow anything to slip past us.\\\"\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He highlighted several incidents around the Olympic village on Sunday.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several incidents\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to a member of Attal's team, the communications chief of the Brazilian delegation was apprehended over operating a drone.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"Attal's team\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"the communications chief\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"the Brazilian delegation\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"a drone\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Any unauthorised drone will be jammed,\\\" said Stephane Groen, France's general in charge of air defence, as Attal visited a control room where an aerial vehicle had been spotted over the Stade de France stadium.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.997274190735678, \"rank\": 0.0027259829861926124, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1057, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Any unauthorised drone\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"Stephane Groen\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"air defence\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"Attal\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"a control room\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"an aerial vehicle\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The defenders' job is particularly tricky as they must avoid the remote vehicles falling while a sporting event is underway.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The defenders' job\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"the remote vehicles\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"a sporting event\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, \\\"if in doubt, we always jam\\\" a drone, Defence Minister Sebastien Lecornu said.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Defence_minister\", \"score\": 0.9999992331325515, \"rank\": 7.66868044923083e-07, \"text\": \"Defence Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Defence_minister\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Defence_minister\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"doubt\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"a drone\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as drone defences, other forms of anti-aircraft defence are in place around Olympic sites.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drone defences\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \"other forms\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"anti-aircraft defence\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1379}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic sites\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 18,000 French troops have been deployed to secure the Olympics, 11,000 of them in the Ile-de-France region around Paris.\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1417, \"end\": 1423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9965765539017346, \"rank\": 0.0016841284208323364, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1524, \"end\": 1529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\":